{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/2014-02-03-word-lookup-in-a-dictionary/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><strong>What method would you use to look up a word in a dictionary ?</strong></p>\n<p>This is a classic binary search algorithm:</p>\n<div id=\"codeSnippetWrapper\">\n<div id=\"codeSnippet\" style=\"overflow:visible;font-size:8pt;font-family:'Courier New', courier, monospace;color:black;direction:ltr;text-align:left;line-height:12pt;width:100%;background-color:#f4f4f4;border-style:none;padding:0;\">\n<pre style=\"overflow:visible;font-size:8pt;font-family:'Courier New', courier, monospace;color:black;direction:ltr;text-align:left;margin:0;line-height:12pt;width:100%;background-color:#f4f4f4;border-style:none;padding:0;\"><span id=\"lnum1\" style=\"color:#606060;\">   1:</span> <span style=\"color:#008000;\">// Assume dict is a sorted dictionary.</span></pre>\n<p><!--CRLF--></p>\n<pre style=\"overflow:visible;font-size:8pt;font-family:'Courier New', courier, monospace;color:black;direction:ltr;text-align:left;margin:0;line-height:12pt;width:100%;background-color:#f4f4f4;border-style:none;padding:0;\"><span id=\"lnum2\" style=\"color:#606060;\">   2:</span> <span style=\"color:#008000;\">// Call with p = 0, q = dict_size - 1;</span></pre>\n<p><!--CRLF--></p>\n<pre style=\"overflow:visible;font-size:8pt;font-family:'Courier New', courier, monospace;color:black;direction:ltr;text-align:left;margin:0;line-height:12pt;width:100%;background-color:#f4f4f4;border-style:none;padding:0;\"><span id=\"lnum3\" style=\"color:#606060;\">   3:</span> <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">bool</span> search(<span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">char</span>** dict, <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">char</span>* s, <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">int</span> p, <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">int</span> q) {</pre>\n<p><!--CRLF--></p>\n<pre style=\"overflow:visible;font-size:8pt;font-family:'Courier New', courier, monospace;color:black;direction:ltr;text-align:left;margin:0;line-height:12pt;width:100%;background-color:#f4f4f4;border-style:none;padding:0;\"><span id=\"lnum4\" style=\"color:#606060;\">   4:</span>   <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">if</span> (p &gt; q) <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">return</span> false;</pre>\n<p><!--CRLF--></p>\n<pre style=\"overflow:visible;font-size:8pt;font-family:'Courier New', courier, monospace;color:black;direction:ltr;text-align:left;margin:0;line-height:12pt;width:100%;background-color:#f4f4f4;border-style:none;padding:0;\"><span id=\"lnum5\" style=\"color:#606060;\">   5:</span>   <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">int</span> mid = (p + q) / 2;</pre>\n<p><!--CRLF--></p>\n<pre style=\"overflow:visible;font-size:8pt;font-family:'Courier New', courier, monospace;color:black;direction:ltr;text-align:left;margin:0;line-height:12pt;width:100%;background-color:#f4f4f4;border-style:none;padding:0;\"><span id=\"lnum6\" style=\"color:#606060;\">   6:</span>   <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">int</span> c = strcmp(dict[mid], s);</pre>\n<p><!--CRLF--></p>\n<pre style=\"overflow:visible;font-size:8pt;font-family:'Courier New', courier, monospace;color:black;direction:ltr;text-align:left;margin:0;line-height:12pt;width:100%;background-color:#f4f4f4;border-style:none;padding:0;\"><span id=\"lnum7\" style=\"color:#606060;\">   7:</span>   <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">if</span> (c &lt; 0) <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">return</span> search(dict, s, p, mid - 1);</pre>\n<p><!--CRLF--></p>\n<pre style=\"overflow:visible;font-size:8pt;font-family:'Courier New', courier, monospace;color:black;direction:ltr;text-align:left;margin:0;line-height:12pt;width:100%;background-color:#f4f4f4;border-style:none;padding:0;\"><span id=\"lnum8\" style=\"color:#606060;\">   8:</span>   <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">if</span> (c &gt; 0) <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">return</span> search(dict, s, mid + 1, q);</pre>\n<p><!--CRLF--></p>\n<pre style=\"overflow:visible;font-size:8pt;font-family:'Courier New', courier, monospace;color:black;direction:ltr;text-align:left;margin:0;line-height:12pt;width:100%;background-color:#f4f4f4;border-style:none;padding:0;\"><span id=\"lnum9\" style=\"color:#606060;\">   9:</span>   <span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">return</span> true;</pre>\n<p><!--CRLF--></p>\n<pre style=\"overflow:visible;font-size:8pt;font-family:'Courier New', courier, monospace;color:black;direction:ltr;text-align:left;margin:0;line-height:12pt;width:100%;background-color:#f4f4f4;border-style:none;padding:0;\"><span id=\"lnum10\" style=\"color:#606060;\">  10:</span> }</pre>\n<p><!--CRLF--></p>\n</div>\n</div>","excerpt":"What method would you use to look up a word in a dictionary ? This is a classic binary search algorithm:","frontmatter":{"date":"03 February, 2014","path":"/blog/2014-02-03-word-lookup-in-a-dictionary/","title":"Word Lookup in a Dictionary"},"fields":{"readingTime":{"text":"2 min read"}}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","63159454"]}